  <div class="summary">今天 AI 圈最大的新闻是 Gemini 3 Deep Think 发布，专攻科研推理。同时 GPT-5.2 在理论物理领域推导出新结果，标志着 AI 辅助科学发现进入新阶段。开源社区方面，GLM-5 和 MiniMax M2.5 各有亮点。</div>
  
  <div class="article">
    <div class="article-num">01</div>
    <div class="article-title"><a href="https://blog.google/technology/ai/gemini-3-deep-think/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Gemini 3 Deep Think: Google 押注科研推理的新模型</a></div>
    <div class="article-source">Google AI Blog</div>
    <div class="article-tldr">Gemini 3 Deep Think 专为复杂科研推理设计，在数学证明和物理推导上超越 o3。采用新的 chain-of-thought 架构，推理深度达 128K token。</div>
    <div class="tags"><span class="tag">模型发布</span><span class="tag">研究</span></div>
    
    <div class="article-excerpt">
      <div class="label">原文摘要</div>
      <div class="text"><p>We are introducing Gemini 3 Deep Think, a model specifically designed for scientific reasoning. Unlike general-purpose models, Deep Think employs a novel recursive reasoning architecture that can sustain coherent chains of thought up to 128K tokens.</p><p>In our benchmarks, Deep Think achieved 94.2% on MATH-500 and 89.1% on a new physics reasoning benchmark, surpassing both o3 and previous Gemini models.</p></div>
    </div>
